'''使徒統緒'''（Apostolic succession），天主教中文译作'''宗徒傳承'''，是指[[基督教|基督教]][[教會|教會]]的聖職是從[[耶稣|耶稣]]的[[十二使徒|十二使徒]]傳承開始代代相傳，通常與聲稱是一系列的[[主教|主教]]有關<ref name="ODCC">F.L. Cross, E.A. Livingstone (editors), ''The Oxford Dictionary of the Christian Church'' (Oxford University Press 2005 ISBN 978-0-19-280290-3), article "apostolic succession"</ref>這一系列的主教，起初被視為[[使徒座|由一個或多個使徒建立的教座]]的主教，但現在被理解為一系列的主教（不論來自那個教座）受其他主教祝聖，而施行祝聖的主教也是以同樣的方式受祝聖，一直追溯至使徒<ref name="ETT">{{cite web |url=http://www.google.com/search?tbm=bks&tbo=1&q=Gonz%C3%A1lez+%22succession+originally+an%22&btnG= |title=Justo L. González, ''Essential Theological Terms'' (Westminster John Knox Press 2005 ISBN 978-0-664-22810-1), p. 15 |publisher=Google.com |date= |accessdate=2013-07-18 |archive-date=2021-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211027175041/http://www.google.com/search?tbm=bks&tbo=1&q=Gonz%C3%A1lez+%22succession+originally+an%22&btnG= |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.google.com/search?tbm=bks&tbo=1&q=Elwell+%22each+bishop+as+a+true+successor%22&btnG= |title = Walter A. Elwell, ''Evangelical Dictionary of Theology'' (Baker Academic 2001 ISBN 978-0-8010-2075-9), p. 89 |publisher = Google.com |date =  |accessdate = 2013-07-18 |archive-date = 2021-05-29 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210529010407/http://www.google.com/search?tbm=bks&tbo=1&q=Elwell+%22each+bishop+as+a+true+successor%22&btnG= |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

使徒統緒也可以理解成從使徒至今的教義連續性<ref>[http://books.google.com/books?id=y_RpbmWNfHcC&pg=PA25&lpg=PA25&dq=%22apostolic+succession%22+anglican&source=bl&ots=TUICDSwWqB&sig=pNp6s1xOVsvx9f4019oYaO5xnL0&hl=en&sa=X&ei=NvhRUM6iDsiJhQf0pYHgBg&ved=0CD4Q6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=%22apostolic%20succession%22%20anglican&f=false Donald S. Armentrout, Robert Boak Slocum ''An Episcopal Dictionary of the Church'' (Church Publishing 1999 ISBN 9780898692112), p. 25] or</ref>。例如，英國[[循道宗|循道宗]]會議將「真實連續」定為「基督經歷的連續，同一靈所賜的團契，屬於一主的連續，訊息的持續宣告，使命的持續領受……<ref name="autogenerated229">Jay, Eric G. ''The Church''. John Knox press: 1980, p.229</ref>」。

一些人視[[按手禮|按手禮]]為使徒統緒的重要部分，因[[新約聖經|新約聖經]]提及個人的使徒傳承（例如從[[保羅|保羅]]到[[提摩太|提摩太]]和[[提多|提多]]）。他們也認為早期教會書信，特別是[[聖紀文|聖紀文]]書信<ref>Adam, Karl. ''The Spirit of Catholicism'' Doubleday & C°, Inc: 1957 p. 20</ref>。紀文特別提到，使徒委派主教為繼承人，並指示主教也應照樣委派繼承人，因此，這樣的教會領袖不能無故罷免。此外，提倡主教擁有個人使徒傳承的人指出，早教統一的教會(431年前)普遍奉行這規定。

很多[[新教|新教]]教派（包括[[信義宗|信義宗]]和[[歸正宗|歸正宗]]）否定使徒統緒的必要<ref name="ODCC" /><ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.questia.com/library/encyclopedia/apostolic_succession.jsp |title = "Apostolic Succession" in ''The Columbia Encyclopedia'', Sixth Edition (Columbia University Press 2004) |publisher = Questia.com |date =  |accessdate = 2013-07-18 |archive-date = 2011-06-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110604100120/http://www.questia.com/library/encyclopedia/apostolic_succession.jsp |dead-url = no }}</ref>，並質疑這些歷史聲稱的真實性。

== 使徒座 ==
{{tsl|en|Apostolic see|使徒座}}是指宣稱自身是由一個或多個[[使徒|使徒]]所建立起來，維繫和傳承該使徒權威、教義和宗教實踐傳統的重要[[主教座|主教座]]。列表如下：
 
'''[[五大宗主教區|五大宗主教區]]'''
* [[聖座|聖座]]：是[[羅馬主教|羅馬主教]]（即众所周知的[[教宗|教宗]]）的{{link-en|教務職權|Ecclesiastical jurisdiction}}，也是[[天主教會|天主教會]]内超乎众教座之上的[[主教教座|主教教座]]，承繼自使徒之首[[彼得_(使徒)|彼得]]（伯多祿）和[[保羅|保羅]]（保祿）<ref>{{cite book|author1=St. Irenaeus|title=Adversus Haereses|year=1907|url=https://archive.org/details/adversushaerese00irengoog|quote=Because it would be too long in such a volume as this to enumerate the successions of all the churches, we point to the tradition of that very great and very ancient and universally known Church, which was founded and established at Rome, by the two most glorious Apostles, Peter and Paul: we point I say, to the tradition which this Church has from the Apostles, and to her faith proclaimed to men which comes down to our time through the succession of her bishops, and so we put to shame . . . all who assemble in unauthorized meetings. For with this Church, because of its superior authority, every Church must agree — that is the faithful everywhere — in communion with which Church the tradition of the Apostles has been always preserved by those who are everywhere}}</ref>。
* [[君士坦丁堡普世牧首區|君士坦丁堡普世牧首區]]：是[[東正教會|東正教會]]的首席大主教區，最高領袖稱為[[君士坦丁堡普世牧首|君士坦丁堡普世牧首]]，承繼自使徒[[聖安德烈|安德烈]]（安德肋）。
* [[亞歷山大港|亞歷山大港]]教區：是[[亞歷山大科普特正教會|亞歷山大科普特正教會]]和{{tsl|en|Greek Orthodox Patriarchate of Alexandria and all Africa|亞歷山大及全非洲地區東正教會}}的教區，最高領袖稱為[[亞歷山大港牧首|亞歷山大港牧首]]，承繼自使徒[[聖馬爾谷|馬可]]（馬爾-{谷}-）。<ref>{{cite web|title=St. Mark The Apostle, Evangelist|url=http://www.copticchurch.net/topics/synexarion/mark.html|accessdate=2017-10-28|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226060330/http://www.copticchurch.net/topics/synexarion/mark.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* [[安提阿|安提阿]]教區：是[[安條克希臘正教會|安提阿正教會]]（現駐[[大馬士革|大馬士革]]），[[默基特希臘禮天主教會|默基特希臘禮天主教會]]（現駐[[大馬士革|大馬士革]]），[[敘利亞東方正統教會|敘利亞東方正統教會]]（現駐[[大馬士革|大馬士革]]），[[敘利亞禮天主教會|敘利亞禮天主教會]]（現駐[[貝魯特|貝魯特]]），[[馬龍尼禮教會|馬龍尼禮教會]]（現駐{{tsl|en|Bkerké|貝凱克}}）的教區，最高領袖稱為[[安提阿牧首|安提阿牧首]]，承繼自使徒之首[[彼得_(使徒)|彼得]]（伯多祿）和[[保羅|保羅]]（保祿）<ref>{{cite web|title=The Patriarchate of Antioch: Founded by Saints Peter and Paul|url=http://antiochian.org/patofant|quote=Ignatius was the second successor to Peter and may actually have been consecrated by that Apostle or Saint Paul.|access-date=2017-10-28|archive-date=2021-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423182222/https://www.antiochian.org/patofant|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*[[耶路撒冷|耶路撒冷]]教區：是{{tsl|en|Greek Orthodox Church of Jerusalem|耶路撒冷正教會}}的首席大主教區，最高領袖稱為[[耶路撒冷牧首|耶路撒冷牧首]]，承繼自使徒[[公義者雅各|公義者雅各]]（雅各伯）<ref>{{cite web|title=305 Chapter XIX.—The Episcopal Chair of James|url=http://www.ccel.org/ccel/schaff/npnf201.iii.xii.xx.html|access-date=2017-10-28|archive-date=2021-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211112090250/https://www.ccel.org/ccel/schaff/npnf201.iii.xii.xx.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

'''其他教區'''
* [[賽普勒斯教會|賽普勒斯教會]]，承繼自使徒[[保羅|保羅]]（保祿）和[[巴拿巴|巴拿巴]]（巴爾納伯）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.churchofcyprus.org.cy/article.php?articleID=89 |title=Cyprian Orthodox Church Official Website |publisher=Churchofcyprus.org.cy |accessdate=26 July 2011 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110723150729/http://www.churchofcyprus.org.cy/article.php?articleID=89 |archivedate=2011-07-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，自431年成為[[東正教自主教會|東正教自主教會]]
